                    <h2>Overview: Accurate &amp; Fair Player Rankings for Street Fighter 6</h2>
                    <p>
                        Our FGC ranking system provides an accurate and current reflection of player skill and performance specifically for Street Fighter 6 (SF6). It ranks players based on their top results from sanctioned offline tournaments worldwide, rewarding consistent excellence and recent achievements. You can view the <a href="/">current player rankings here</a>.
                    </p>
